title: A257 crash: Motorcyclist dies in crash near Wingham
title_page: A257 crash: Motorcyclist dies in crash near Wingham - BBC News
maintext:
A motorcyclist has died in a crash on the A257 in Kent.
At about 08:30 GMT on Tuesday, a Yamaha motorcycle was involved in a crash with a grey Lexus car in Shatterling, between Wingham and Ash, Kent Police said.
The motorcyclist, a man in his 30s, died at the scene and the road was closed until about 16:00, police added.
Kent Police's serious collision investigation unit is carrying out enquiries and urging anyone with information to contact them.
